X,Y
n
A^k X = B^k Y
k=1,2,...,2n
X = Y
C= \begin{pmatrix} A & 0 \\0 & B \\ \end{pmatrix} \,.
C
C^{-1}= \begin{pmatrix} A^{-1} & 0 \\0 & B^{-1} \\ \end{pmatrix} \,.
P(x)=x^{2n}+a_{2n-1}x^{2n-1}+....+a_0
C
C
a_0 \neq 0
I_{2n}=-\frac{1}{a_0} [ C^{2n}+a_{2n-1}C^{2n-1}+....+a_1C] \,.
Q(x)=-\frac{1}{a_0} [ x^{2n}+a_{2n-1}x^{2n-1}+....+a_1x] \,.
Q(C)=I_{2n}
C
Q(A)=Q(B)=I_n
A^kX=B^kY, \forall 1 \leq k \leq 2n
Q(A)X=Q(B)Y
X=Y
X=I_nX=Q(A)X=-\frac{1}{a_0} [ A^{2n}X+a_{2n-1}A^{2n-1}X+....+a_1AX]=-\frac{1}{a_0} [ B^{2n}Y+a_{2n-1}B^{2n-1}Y+....+a_1BY]=Q(B)Y=I_nY=Y \,.
